      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, tear your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> with most of your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>(save a little for garnish!) and cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
