    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[180ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>mustard stock</strong></p>",
